1.    Pull the power cord from the docking station
 
 
2.    Make sure no power cord is connected to the laptop directly.
 
 
3.    Remove any USB connections from the laptop.
 
 
4.    Wait 5 minutes.
 
 
5.    Reconnect power to the docking station.
 
  
6.    Dock laptop.
 
 
7.    Power up laptop.
 
 
